# Git workflow

- Use the terminal to manage the local Git repository.
- Make small, atomic commits after each completed feature or logical change.
- Use [Conventional Commits](https://www.conventionalcommits.org/) (e.g. `feat: add stat parser`, `fix: cross-sell UI bug`).
- Do not push to remotes unless the user explicitly asks; default is local commits only.
